). This cortical microtubule stabilizing activity is regulated at least in part by phosphatidylinositol 3-kinase signaling. Also performs a similar stabilizing function at the kinetochore which is essential for the bipolar alignment of chromosomes on the mitotic spindle (PubMed:16866869, PubMed:16914514). Acts as a mediator of ERBB2- dependent stabilization of microtubules at the cell cortex. {ECO:0000269|PubMed:11290329, ECO:0000269|PubMed:15631994, ECO:0000269|PubMed:16824950, ECO:0000269|PubMed:16866869, ECO:0000269|PubMed:16914514, ECO:0000269|PubMed:17543864, ECO:0000269|PubMed:20937854, ECO:0000269|PubMed:26003921}."], "subcellular_locations": [{"location": "Cytoplasm", "source": "uniprot", "termSL": "SL-0086", "labelSL": "Cellular component"}, {"location": "Chromosome", "source": "uniprot", "termSL": "SL-0468", "labelSL": "Cellular component"}, {"location": "Golgi apparatus", "source": "uniprot", "termSL": "SL-0132", "labelSL": "Cellular component"}, {"location": "Cell membrane", "source": "uniprot", "termSL": "SL-0039", "labelSL": "Cellular component"}, {"location": "Cell projection", "source": "uniprot", "termSL": "SL-0280", "labelSL": "Cellular component"}, {"location": "Golgi apparatus", "source": "HPA_main", "termSL": "SL-0132", "labelSL": "Golgi apparatus"}, {"location": "Cytosol", "source": "HPA_additional", "termSL": "SL-0091", "labelSL": "Cytosol"}], "obsolete_symbols": [], "obsolete_names": [], "protein_ids": [{"id": "O75122", "source": "uniprot_swissprot"}, {"id": "A0A0U1RQI6", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "A0A804HJG7", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "B3KR06", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "C9J668", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "D6RBU8", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "E3W994", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "E7ENG2", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "E7ERI8", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "E7EW49", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "H7C4I5", "source": "uniprot_trembl"}, {"id": "H7C4M5", "source": "unip